{"tid":1381703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求文宣協助] 發夢急救員想搵文宣幫手","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:46:02.000Z","uid":281759,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6b647ba283af19ec3a0ffa154c01ed6569e31ef3","tid":1381703,"uid":281759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"發夢急救嗰陣唔太暢順<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望文宣能夠協助</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.</span> 可唔可以整張嘢, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尋找可以借用地方+借用清水, 沖洗皮膚嘅商店/地方</span><br />\n(e.g.廁所, 後巷+水喉)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. </span>夾整張嘢比<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>前線</strong></span>及<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>中線</strong></span>:<br />\n==== 希望佢哋背襄要有以下物品:<br />\na.    一支大生理鹽水<br />\nb.    幾支細生理鹽水(眼睛自救)<br />\nc.    一支唔飲嘅水 (畀急救員幫你清嘢 或 極口渴時嘅後備水 - <span style=\"font-size: small;\">注意, 飲用過就唔可以作醫療用圖</span>)<br />\nd.    五包紅水色清毒藥水 (透明袋長條型嗰啲)<br />\ne.    三兩包敷料 (包裝係一個正方型膠袋入住, 裡面有5張嗰啲)<br />\nf.    一個冰包 (上網搵 Ice pack / instant cold pack)<br />\n==== 原因: 急救員真係拎唔到咁多嘢周圍走, 如果一人拎一啲可以幫助急救員支緩更多傷者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.</span> 夾整張嘢比<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>中線</strong></span>及<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>後線</strong></span>:<br />\n==== 希望能夠協助前線急救物資協調:<br />\n-----------&gt; <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>中線</strong></span>幫手從<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>後線</strong></span>拎急救物資畀<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>前線急救員</strong></span><br />\n-----------&gt; <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>後線</strong></span>睇吓有冇辨法每人揹多幾支, 做個流動水站<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>注意 注意 注意</strong><br />\n物資<strong>唔好太早</strong>畀急救員!<br />\n出咗兩三輪胡椒/催淚之後嘅幾個小時係急救員最需要不停哋補水嘅時候!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n==== 原因: 最快用晒嘅係水 (生理鹽水/乾淨未飲過嘅飲用水/一般洗手嘅水喉水)<br />\n==== 急救員真係拎唔到咁多嘢周圍走, 如果一人拎一啲可以幫助急救員支緩更多傷者<br />\n-----------&gt; Side note:<br />\n生理鹽水/乾淨未飲過嘅飲用水 --&gt; 主要處理傷口<br />\n一般洗手嘅水喉水 --&gt; 大範圍清洗化學物<br />\n<br />\n真心, 需要大家幫幫手!!"},{"pid":"feb9012e85d83944dcc5c79f8c78e11eb2fe27da","tid":1381703,"uid":281759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n我知我P牌, 幫個手吖..."},{"pid":"4b2b0ae41c00c8a30c6fb2f645a5339aee7afd2c","tid":1381703,"uid":117264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff5278c1bec4a29a0625e0b732a10fda7c0255a","tid":1381703,"uid":283468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"481c51da7bdf886518297e495e06849f37a5867d","tid":1381703,"uid":117264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4fe704597121b5fd8420b27ca5758856ca081d","tid":1381703,"uid":117264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d4a390f8ae5c408c2cb481a0dc19f51bfb2db0","tid":1381703,"uid":117264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye